OL,3,CFire Service marks a year since fatal
OL,4,Cblaze at Bicester business park
OL,6,FA memorial service will be held today
OL,7,Fto remember the lives of three people
OL,8,Fwho died in a fire at a Oxfordshire
OL,9,Fbusiness park last year.
OL,11,FFriday marks the first anniversary of
OL,12,Fthe fire at Bicester Motion, which
OL,13,Fkilled firefighters Jennie Logan, 30,
OL,14,Fand Martyn Sadler, 38, as well as 57
OL,15,Fyear old local businessman Dave
OL,16,FChester.
OL,18,FTwo other firefighters were also
OL,19,Fseriously injured in the incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
