OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778854269
OL,3,CFire Service marks a year since fatal
OL,4,Cblaze at Bicester business park
OL,6,FCrews from across Oxfordshire Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service (OFRS) have been
OL,8,Finvited to attend a private service at
OL,9,FSt Edburg's Church.
OL,11,FA memorial garden will also be opened
OL,12,Fin memory of the victims at Bicester
OL,13,FFire Station.
OL,15,FThames Valley Police and the Health
OL,16,Fand Safety Executive (HSE) are
OL,17,Fcontinuing to investigate what caused
OL,18,Fthe fire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
