OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778854269
OL,3,CFire Service marks a year since fatal
OL,4,Cblaze at Bicester business park
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOFRS Chief Fire Officer Rob MacDougall
OL,12,Fpaid tribute to the victims, ahead of
OL,13,Fthe anniversary, saying: "As we
OL,14,Fapproach one year since the
OL,15,Fheartbreaking event on 15th May 2025
OL,16,Fat Bicester Motion, I wanted to take a
OL,17,Fmoment to pay tribute to Jennie Logan,
OL,18,FMartyn Sadler and Dave Chester.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
