FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778854269
OL,3,CFire Service marks a year since fatal
OL,4,Cblaze at Bicester business park
OL,6,F"That evening, we lost two of our
OL,7,Ffriends and colleagues, Firefighters
OL,8,FJennie and Martyn - alongside Dave, a
OL,9,Fwellknown and valued member of the
OL,10,FBicester community.
OL,12,F"Their loss is something that stays
OL,13,Fwith all of us.
OL,15,F"We know how deeply cared for, loved
OL,16,Fand respected Jennie, Martyn and Dave
OL,17,Fwere to everyone who knew them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
